@zakfrost super double strike exists already as well ([Mage Slayer](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Mage Slayer)). it deals pre first strike damage, **before blockers are even declared.** it then proceeds to deal normal combat damage. put it on a creature with double strike and it has triple strike.  

also,  
@blindthrall there is an enchantment which gives your definition of "super flying", [Treetop Bracers](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Treetop Bracers). there are also other things with that, but i'm lazy.
